			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			ATTENTION ALL ROGUES<BR>
<BR>
************************************************<BR>
<BR>
It has been decided that the maximum price to pay for any ravenscale armor is 50 plat. This number should only be reached after a long debate on prices as to why we should pay more than 5 plat. <BR>
<BR>
There will be no market for the pathetic casters that want to farm our equipment. This rule holds for all classes and races as many casters have multiple characters and will transfer it to a mule to try and get around our standing. There are already 1000 rogues that have aggreed to this. If you give in and pay more it is no one's fault but your own when the other pieces you want are being sold like ruby. We will provide no market for them and to leave us to our own. <BR>
<BR>
There are alreayd reports of casters doing the 'ninja loot' and trying to sell the equipment to their own party. Which they were promtply disbanded, and laughed out of the zone. That wizard will not be grouped with anymore. The shaman that tried to go out and sell his wares found an opening bid of 5 plat, and at 50 plat no one would rise. he left the zone. They will give up when they learn we are adamant about this. <BR>
<BR>
We have been the ignored and inderpowered for our entire careers. It is time to show them that they cannot dictate or try to rob a rogue. If anyone is a thief in the game it is us. Dont let them win. in a few weeks we will all have the armor. We are the ONLY ones that can use it. Be patient, and hold to our prices, and all will be well. Fold, give into the finger wagglers, and you will soon be told to trade some obscene items and money for armor that only you can use.<BR>
<BR>
Stand together.<BR>
<BR>
-Legna<BR>
<BR>
***********************************************<BR>
<BR>
I couldn't agree with Legna more!! Do not pay more than 50pp for ANY raven scale armor. United we will stand!! Do not allow campers to sell our Armour for astounding prices!!<BR>
<BR>
IT ENDS HERE!!<BR>
<BR>
Kyenn - Bristlebane<BR>
